title: Tattoo, Piercing and Other Service Horror Stories
description:
It takes work to look this good, but sometimes the work is the problem. This week, Tasia and Camo swap stories about the tattoos they love and hate, sometimes taking days to complete, bad eyebrow threading that takes a little too much off the top and much more. Plus, in a new segment, Tasia and Camo prank call a Waffle House with an elderly character that's having stomach issues.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
